{"tid":1127400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又來料！據悉滙控研節省成本措施 或包括削減職位","createTime":"2019-04-27T05:49:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T13:36:37.000Z","uid":19454,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"a905377904a69def03a077ee80da79a8f5f06a71","tid":1127400,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:49:11.000Z","msg":"有消息指，滙豐控股正研究節省成本措施，當中可能包括削減職位。  滙控去年業績差過市場預期，支出增長仍然較收入快。《彭博》引述消息人士報道，滙控大約400名行政人員上月於香港舉行會議，檢討收入支出不能夠達標原因。行政總裁范寧在會議上批評管理層不稱職。  報道又指，滙控要求個別高層人員設法節省開支，包括裁減職位。消息人士透露，滙控一旦削職，投資銀行部門相信不能倖免，又指受影響員工會於年中左右收到通知。  滙控將於下星期五公布今年第一季業績<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/finance/5cc390cfe603835d7fcaf041/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Ffinance%2F5cc390cfe603835d7fcaf041%2F&d=wHiIeFeeqtLxwJ75m5qcs4ICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=b173c91c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/finance/5cc390cfe603835d7fcaf041/</a>"},{"pid":"ab5b8750b499f78bf6f9617b570eccc88e8cf799","tid":1127400,"uid":19454,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:49:22.000Z","msg":"IT First<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9de50c34198c63c8cd6714c84d2f150ff60d2128","tid":1127400,"uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:50:34.000Z","msg":"檢討收入支出不能夠達標原因<br />\n檢討收入支出不能夠達標原因<br />\n檢討收入支出不能夠達標原因<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n肯定又係IT惹的禍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ed275b5c8a56ad3e951c713b81513965c251e4","tid":1127400,"uid":101945,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:51:14.000Z","msg":"HK FIRST<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid